# LEVEL 3 IMPLEMENTATION: BUILDING INTERMEDIATE FEATURES

> **TL;DR:** This guide focuses on the systematic implementation of a planned and designed Level 3 feature using **Test-Driven Development (TDD)**. It emphasizes writing tests FIRST, then implementing modules to pass those tests, strict adherence to creative decisions and the style guide, integration with existing systems, and thorough feature-specific testing.

